403
00:31:32,892 --> 00:31:34,093
U redu je, sve je ok!

404
00:31:34,145 --> 00:31:35,645
Hajde "Petlovi"!
-Napred "Petlovi"!

405
00:31:39,149 --> 00:31:40,349
Idemo, momci!

406
00:31:40,609 --> 00:31:41,609
Idemo do kraja...

407
00:31:46,448 --> 00:31:47,447
Cuvaj, cuvaj...

408
00:31:55,624 --> 00:31:58,120
