Ne zanima me ko je poceo, idi sad.

414
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:17,109
Tajm-aut. Dolazite ovamo! Ovamo!

415
00:32:21,537 --> 00:32:25,887
Ti... a ti...

416
00:32:26,386 --> 00:32:33,487
